      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s looking for a new home! It\u2019s been super well-loved and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for your daily commutes or weekend adventures. It runs smoothly and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
