      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 1995 BMW M3, featuring the high-revving S50 inline-six powerplant paired with a crisp 5-speed manual transmission. This E36 chassis remains structurally sound with a sorted suspension geometry utilizing Bilstein B8 dampers and reinforced subframe points. The drivetrain benefits from a factory-spec 3.15 limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Recent mechanical preventative maintenance includes a full cooling system refresh\u2014addressing the water pump and expansion tank\u2014alongside a recalibrated VANOS unit for linear power delivery. It sits on genuine lightweight Style 24 forged wheels. While showing honest patina consistent with its age, the compression across all cylinders remains within tight tolerances, making this a mechanically robust example ready for the apex.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
