    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents an excellent opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, accented by professional detailing; however, close inspection reveals minor road-pepper on the front bumper and a small, shallow scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the interior is exceptionally clean and smoke-free. The leather surfaces are soft and intact, with only light character creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Every button, switch, and digital display functions perfectly, including the cold AC and the upgraded infotainment system. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs whisper-quiet. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and a fresh set of tires installed less than 2,000 miles ago. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains firm yet comfortable. I have a comprehensive folder of service history and receipts ready for the next owner to review, ensuring total transparency in this sale.",
      "price": 33500.0,
